# 🌐 AWS VPC Hands-On Project

## 📌 Overview

This project focuses on Amazon VPC (Virtual Private Cloud), which allows users to create a secure and isolated virtual network environment inside AWS.

The project covers VPC creation, subnets, routing, gateways, security configurations, and networking fundamentals used in real-world cloud infrastructures.

